profile_positions.description:
• collecting and preparing target variables from secondary data from various sources (World Governance Indicators; Polity 4 project; World Bank Data; CIRI Human Rights Data Project; UNDP; Indices of Social Development; Media Sustainability; Reporters Without Borders; and US-Based Organisation Freedom House);
• Conducting Granger-causality test for a binary regression analysis;
• Conducting cross-country and panel data analysis with endogeneity checks and fixed-effects (country fixed effects, time-lags, and when possible also IV analysis);
• Providing all the raw data, prepared data and STATA log file in a clear and accessible manner
